title: flutter_neumorphic
introductionEN: A complete, ready to use, Neumorphic ui kit for Flutter. Dark theming compatible & fully customizable.
introductionCN: 一个完整的、随时可用的、用于Flutter的Neumorphic ui套件。深色主题兼容且完全可定制。

title: getwidget
introductionEN: GetWidget is open source library that come with pre-build 1000+ UI components. It makes development faster & more enjoyable. You can customize the component as per your need.
introductionCN: GetWidget是一个开源库，带有预构建的1000多个UI组件。它使开发更快，更愉快。您可以根据需要自定义组件。
